full_text: Screened by NARA, 9/18/2023 OPTIONAL FORM NO. 10 3010-104 UNITED STATES GOVERNMENT Memorandum TO : Associate Commissioner, Management DATE: August 31, 1966 Central Office (via Regional Office) FROM : District Director, Boston, Mass. The alien has never been the beneficiary of XX a Private Bill.
